                      "value": "<div class=\"themePopularSteerWrap\">\n    <div class=\"themeSteerTitle\">\n        <h3>Why Buy Genuine Nissan Accessories?</h3>\n    </div>\n    <ul class=\"themeSteerList\">\n        <li>\n            <div class=\"themeSteerListCard\">\n                <div class=\"themeSteerListImg\">\n                    <img src=\"https://rparts-sites.s3.amazonaws.com/ddf1a4688f481343d29071cefb36dbca/design/why/safety.avif\" alt=\"Safety Icon\">\n                </div>\n                <h4>Compatibility in, Guesswork Out</h4>\n                <p>From emblems to <a href=\"/part-categories/exterior/roof-rails\">roof racks</a>, our accessories come guaranteed to fit your <a href=\"/v-nissan\">Nissan</a>, work right the first time, and look the part. A lot of aftermarket accessories can't always say the same.</p>\n            </div>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n            <div class=\"themeSteerListCard\">\n                <div class=\"themeSteerListImg\">\n                    <img src=\"https://rparts-sites.s3.amazonaws.com/ddf1a4688f481343d29071cefb36dbca/design/why/reli.avif\" alt=\"Reliability Icon\">\n                </div>\n                <h4>Nissan Quality Assured</h4>\n                <p>Genuine OEM means genuine Nissan -- accessories expertly crafted to the excellent standards you're familiar with. Expect nothing less.</p>\n            </div>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n            <div class=\"themeSteerListCard\">\n                <div class=\"themeSteerListImg\">\n                    <img src=\"https://rparts-sites.s3.amazonaws.com/ddf1a4688f481343d29071cefb36dbca/design/why/perfect.avif\" alt=\"Perfect Fit Icon\">\n                </div>\n                <h4>Expertise at Your Service</h4>\n                <p>Nissan Genuine Parts and Accessories are made to perfectly fit your vehicle ensuring it runs at its optimum level, and is ready for any adventure.</p>\n            </div>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n            <div class=\"themeSteerListCard\">\n                <div class=\"themeSteerListImg\">\n                    <img src=\"https://rparts-sites.s3.amazonaws.com/ddf1a4688f481343d29071cefb36dbca/design/why/future.avif\" alt=\"Future Proof Icon\">\n                </div>\n                <h4>Peace of Mind Included</h4>\n                <p>Buy with confidence -- genuine Nissan accessories are almost always warranty-backed. Using them won't void your factory warranty, either. That's an investment, covered.</p>\n            </div>\n        </li>\n    </ul>\n</div>"
